00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:26,298
You!

176
00:14:26,365 --> 00:14:28,067
Shh! Stay quiet!

177
00:14:28,634 --> 00:14:31,136
Haruto?

178
00:14:31,203 --> 00:14:32,304
Hey!

179
00:14:32,371 --> 00:14:34,206
Haruto!

180
00:14:36,075 --> 00:14:39,078
