181
00:14:40,279 --> 00:14:41,113
Yes.

182
00:14:41,180 --> 00:14:42,982
Pardon me.

183
00:14:43,048 --> 00:14:45,751
Um, have you seen Haruto?

184
00:14:46,852 --> 00:14:47,686
Haruto?

185
00:14:47,753 --> 00:14:50,356
Um, he's a boy wearing white pajamas.

186
00:14:54,159 --> 00:14:54,994
