188
00:15:10,509 --> 00:15:11,343
Thank you!

189
00:15:11,410 --> 00:15:13,646
Um…

190
00:15:15,881 --> 00:15:16,882
Excuse me!

191
00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:19,485
Can I help you?

192
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:23,489
I think I just smelled Haruto.

193
00:15:24,590 --> 00:15:25,424
What?

194
00:15:25,491 --> 00:15:26,992
Maybe it was just me.

195
00:15:28,027 --> 00:15:28,861
Yes.

196
00:15:30,396 --> 00:15:31,864
Pardon me.

197
